---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import H3 from "../components/text/H3.astro"
import P from "../components/text/P.astro"
import ProfileImage from "../components/ProfileImage.astro"
import qiyuanImage from "../assets/qiyuan.jpg"
import qiyuanCropped from "../assets/qiyuan_cropped.jpg"
---

<section class="pt-20 xl:w-4/5">
	<H3 className="mb-12">About Me</H3>

	<div class="flex flex-col gap-12 md:flex-row">
		<!-- Text Content -->
		<div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
			<P>
				Hey! I'm Qiyuan, a software engineer with a passion for building
				thoughtful, efficient web applications. My journey into tech
				started with a background in mathematics and computer science,
				which gave me a strong foundation in problem-solving and logical
				thinking.
			</P>

			<P>
				I enjoy working across the full stackâ€”from designing robust
				backend systems to crafting intuitive user interfaces. Whether
				it's optimizing performance, refactoring legacy code, or
				building new features from scratch, I'm always looking for ways
				to write clean, maintainable code.
			</P>

			<P>
				Here are a few technologies I've been working with recently:
			</P>

			<ul
				class="text-muted marker:text-accent grid w-max list-disc grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-2 pl-4 text-sm"
			>
				<li>TypeScript</li>
				<li>React</li>
				<li>Tailwind</li>
				<li>Node.js</li>
				<li>Next.js</li>
				<li>Python</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<!-- Image -->
		<div class="flex flex-col items-center md:w-1/3">
			<ProfileImage
				src={qiyuanCropped}
				alt="Qiyuan Chen"
				className="block w-60 md:hidden"
			/>
			<ProfileImage
				src={qiyuanImage}
				alt="Qiyuan Chen"
				className="hidden md:block md:w-48 lg:w-56 xl:w-64"
			/>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
